CPUE near and far the Phoenix Islands Protected Area

data_PIPA.Rd

A data.frame with 663 rows and 6 columns:

time

Numeric - Number of year until / since the the intervention takes place

lat

Numeric - Latitude indicating centroid of the grid cell

lon

Numeric - Longitude indicating centroid of the grid cell

near

Logical - `TRUE`, indicates the observation comes from inside the MPA

post

Logical - `TRUE` indicates the observation comes from the period after the intervention took place

cpue

Numeric - Catch-per-unit-effort meassured in metric tons per fishing set

Usage

data_PIPA

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 663 rows and 6 columns.

Details

Panel data with CPUE data from near and far from the boundaries of the Phoenix Islands Protected Area.
